flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "16C2C0BD42C39EFB4563AD958FE3A1CD", "Your Mayor knows well the dangers of the Arboreal Spider. These creatures live high in the trees, remaining unseen and unnoticed until their homes are destroyed by rampant logging. Then they suddenly swarm, overwhelming hapless lumberfolk. Go find their haunts, and thin their numbers.")
